# Sovrunn Architecture Rules

Use source documents in `docs/architecture/`, `docs/resource-specs/`, `docs/api/`, and the current feature file.

Resource model:

```text
metadata = identity and classification
spec = desired state
status = observed state
operation = lifecycle trace
```

Hierarchy:

```text
Organization -> OrganizationUnit -> Tenant -> Project -> ServiceInstance -> ServiceBinding
ServiceClass -> ServicePlan
Plugin -> Capability
```

Implementation must remain in-memory for Phase 1 unless explicitly approved otherwise.
